name: Pearl, Cylinders & Cloth
description: This is Fizah Rahim's genesis piece on Hic Et Nunc. The artwork explores the thought of creating something purely out of the sheer enjoyment of creation and nothing else. Stripping off unnecessary elements and noise. Stripping it bare. Into simple shapes and just organic flow of a cloth and light refraction play. Edition of 30.  1500 x 1500 px.
